<div class="jumbotron">
	<h1> Organic Chemistry Studying Games</h1>
	<h2 class="text-primary">A series of drills as test prep for organic chemistry.</h2>
	<p id='ast' >*These games require some previous knowledge of principles.</p>
</div>
<div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
	<!-- Indicators -->
	<ol class="carousel-indicators">
		<li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
		<li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
		<li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
		<li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>
	</ol>

	<!-- Wrapper for slides -->
	<div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
		<div class="item active">
			<div class="game">
				<%= image_tag 'alkanes/methane.png', class:'img-responsive center-block img-thumbnail' %>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="item">
			<div class="game">
				<%= image_tag 'alkenes/zbut2ene.png', class:'img-responsive center-block img-thumbnail' %>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="item">
			<div class="game">
				<%= image_tag 'cyclohexane_chair_colour.png', class:'img-responsive center-block img-thumbnail' %>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="item">
			<div class="game">
				<%= image_tag 'newman_projection_of_propane.png', class:'img-responsive center-block img-thumbnail' %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- Controls -->
	<a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
	<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
	<span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
	</a>
	<a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
	<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
	<span class="sr-only">Next</span>
	</a>
</div>
<div class ='info_section'>
	<div class="info">
		<h2><%= link_to 'Name that Alkane!',alkanes_path%></h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Name the unbranched alkane according to the IUPAC system.</li>
				<li>You have 25 seconds.</li>
				<li>You have three strikes before the game ends.</li>
				<li>A strike is assigned if an incorrect answer is given, or the timer hits 0.</li>
			</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="info">
		<h2><a href="alkenes">Name that Alkene!</a></h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Name the unbranched alkene according to the IUPAC system.</li>
			<li>You have 30 seconds.</li>
			<li>You have three strikes before the game ends.</li>
			<li>Only use the e,z notation for naming (Cahn–Ingold–Prelog priority rules).</li>
			<li>If the double bond is at Carbon #1, no 'e-' or 'z-' is placed before the name.</li>
			<li>The number of the carbon at which the double bond is located is placed after the prefix, but before the suffix.</li>
			<li>Don't forget dashes!</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="info">
		<h2><a href="chairs"> Chair Flips </a></h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Click on a carbon and drag to draw a sidechain into the appropriate position for a chair flip.</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="info">
		<h2><a href="newman"> Newman Projections </a></h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Rotate the back carbon so that the molecule is in its lowest energy conformtion.</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div>